  - Automated PostgreSQL backups
  - Simple backup retention policy
  - Basic restore procedures

  4. Basic Monitoring Alerts - 2-3 hours

  - Essential health check alerts
  - Email/Slack notifications for critical issues
  - Simple uptime monitoring

  Optional but Recommended (1-2 days)

  5. Log Management - 3-4 hours

  - Centralized logging (simple ELK stack or file-based)
  - Log rotation and retention

  6. Performance Tuning - 2-3 hours

  - Database connection pooling
  - Redis caching configuration
  - Frontend build optimization

  7. Security Hardening - 3-4 hours

  - Basic firewall rules
  - Security headers
  - Rate limiting configuration

